{"tid":2036112,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何栢良倡取消限聚令立戴罩令","createTime":"2020-05-26T09:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T09:41:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b7700f0e5943acbaeb339de17c55043c9a8ae0d2","tid":2036112,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:22:36.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200526/QAU2GL5ESSVDS3JVPPKPUWEGXM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FQAU2GL5ESSVDS3JVPPKPUWEGXM%2F&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMAxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=c3949396\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200526%2FQAU2GL5ESSVDS3JVPPKPUWEGXM%2F&h=82ded916\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200526/QAU2GL5ESSVDS3JVPPKPUWEGXM/</a><br />\n<br />\n何栢良倡取消限聚令立戴罩令<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200526/large/1590423884_bf0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200526%2Flarge%2F1590423884_bf0b.jpg&h=90216034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何栢良<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港武漢肺炎昨日錄得連續11日零確診，中三至中五學生明日起分階段復課。港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良昨接受電台訪問時指出，本港自梨木樹家庭群組至今再沒有新增本地個案，認為本地傳播鏈變得穩定，可考慮6月4日後取消限聚令，惟港人仍要戴口罩防疫。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n促強制坐公共交通時戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n何栢良指出，限聚令成效微，「戴口罩先係關鍵」，限聚令與現時泳池重開、復課等措施有牴觸。不過他認為，政府應立例規定市民乘搭公共交通時戴口罩。他指，梨木樹家庭群組仍未找到源頭，不排除是海外回港人士測試「假陰性」或有人家居隔離時不守規矩，令社區出現隱形傳播，因市民戴口罩意識高，未有造成傳播鏈。他又呼籲學生復課不要戴「自私」氣閥式口罩，因為氣閥會將使用者的飛沫排出空氣中，傳播病毒。<br />\n<br />\n不過，特首林鄭月娥另有看法，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n■記者謝明明"},{"pid":"57e085f620d7c17741747eadb0bdb5db9a7fb4fe","tid":2036112,"uid":261095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:25:02.000Z","msg":"大家上Twitter 幫手推「中共大審判日」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2035397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2035397</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"78b7dd18c2d50cbeb77c51b8a483e245700c37de","tid":2036112,"uid":77196,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"你死心啦有蒙面法佢下世都唔會立法限戴口罩"},{"pid":"065b1792acef4209edbce5b1a9b8a2c625c4433e","tid":2036112,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"呢d真係心水清"},{"pid":"eb9ff79b1a368b55036979bc6b29503fff539166","tid":2036112,"uid":44646,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"林奠搵4個專家做顧問<br />\n人地提專業意見又唔跟<br />\n問意見問黎托呀？"},{"pid":"d92ac7ad323c36789ea504c5f8dcfb9dfb1e2be0","tid":2036112,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:36:34.000Z","msg":"冇科學根據同擾民嘅限聚令由佢決定並實施<br />\n有科學根據又唔擾民嘅措施就唔跟，而且一句冇政治考慮就算數<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅人負責領導香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aebfe58d4d2baa36e9c5797ba94bf556257fd72","tid":2036112,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:40:21.000Z","msg":"777: 何柏良？唔聽"},{"pid":"1ee79e3af3058ac9909da3d738d20a98c80a1bd6","tid":2036112,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:40:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1696ee389f319d6362608d3e06c0c60c032cdb43","tid":2036112,"uid":89517,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:41:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f1b799e52664766038586d5d60b0b09cc1fc8ee","tid":2036112,"uid":256783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:41:11.000Z","ms